* Peabo Doue, soccer player
* Matt Drudge, political commentator, creator and editor of the Drudge Report 
* Marc Elrich, Montgomery County Executive
* John Fahey, guitarist; founder of Takoma Records
* Peter Franchot, former Maryland State Comptroller
* Steve Francis, former National Basketball Association player
* Goldie Hawn, actress
*Bowie Kuhn, Commissioner of Baseball from 1969–1984, was born in Takoma Park.
* Denis McDonough, White House chief of staff in the Obama Administration, Secretary of Veterans Affairs in the Biden Administration
* Mona Minkara, chemist at Northeastern University
* Heather Mizeur, former Maryland State Delegate; candidate in Democratic primary for governor in 2014 
* David Moon, Maryland State Delegate, District 20
