* Leeds, England, United Kingdom
* Liège, Belgium
* Nablus, Palestine
* Oujda, Morocco
* Rotterdam, Netherlands
* Saint-Louis, Senegal
* Tlemcen, Algeria
* Turin, Italy
* Valladolid, Spain
* Wrocław, Poland
